These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: water, almond-milk
There 2 different types of food: eggplant, radish
The people have 2 different hobbies: skydiving, cooking
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: family, superhero
1. the person watching family movies is not to the right of the person eating radish##8
2. the person eating radish is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##5
3. the person drinking water is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |
| Beverage      | almond-milk     | water      |
| Food          | radish | eggplant    |
| Hobby         | cooking   | skydiving |
| Movie-Genre   | family  | superhero      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, tea
The people have 2 different hobbies: fishing, photography
The people have 2 different jobs:  lawyer, police-officer
The people use 2 different means of transport: ship, bike
1. the person drinking tea is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is somewhere to the left of the lawyer##5
3. the police-officer is not to the right of the lawyer##8
4. the person driving the ship is not the person who's hobby is photography##6

.:: Answer ::.
|             |         1          |      2      |
| Beverage    | coffee        | tea    |
| Hobby       | fishing         | photography |
| Job         | police-officer | lawyer   |
| Transport   | ship               | bike  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-3::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: documentary, time-travel
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: reggae, pop
There are 2 different nationalities: turkish, colombian
2 different pets are kept: frog, fish
1. the turkish is in an odd position##4
2. the colombian is not to the right of the owner of the fish##8
3. the fan of reggae is somewhere to the left of the person watching time-travel movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary       | time-travel |
| Music-Genre   | reggae       | pop    |
| Nationality   | turkish | colombian |
| Pet           | frog        | fish   |

 #################################

 
