2. the person driving the quad-bike is the person driving the quad-bike##1
3. the person eating grapefruit is somewhere to the right of the engineer##5
4. the person driving the quad-bike is not to the right of the person driving the skateboard##8
5. the person driving the skateboard is not to the left of the person eating grapefruit##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |         2          |
